### Test Project Summary and RSVP Stats Endpoints
### Prerequisites: Login and get token first

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
@projectId = YOUR_PROJECT_ID
@eventId = YOUR_EVENT_ID

### 1. Get Project Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Response should include:
# {
#   "done": 0,              // Tasks completed in last 7 days
#   "updated": 0,           // Tasks updated in last 7 days
#   "created": 0,           // Tasks created in last 7 days
#   "due": 0,               // Tasks due in next 7 days
#   "statusOverview": {
#     "period": "last 14 days",
#     "total": 3,
#     "toDo": 3,            // TO_DO status
#     "inProgress": 0,      // IN_PROGRESS status
#     "inReview": 0,        // IN_REVIEW status
#     "done": 0             // DONE status
#   }
# }

###

### 2. Get RSVP Stats for Event
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}/rsvp-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Response should include:
# {
#   "eventId": "uuid",
#   "eventTitle": "Sprint Planning",
#   "stats": {
#     "total": 5,
#     "accepted": 3,
#     "declined": 1,
#     "tentative": 1,
#     "invited": 0,
#     "noResponse": 0
#   },
#   "participants": {
#     "ACCEPTED": [
#       {
#         "email": "user1@example.com",
#         "name": "User One",
#         "avatar": "https://..."
#       }
#     ],
#     "DECLINED": [...],
#     "TENTATIVE": [...],
#     "INVITED": [...],
#     "NO_RESPONSE": [...]
#   }
# }

###

### 3. Update Participant RSVP Status (for testing)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}/participants/user@example.com/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACCEPTED"
}

### Available status values: ACCEPTED, DECLINED, TENTATIVE

###

### 4. Get Event with Participants
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Create Test Event with Participants
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "title": "Test Meeting for RSVP",
  "description": "Testing RSVP stats endpoint",
  "date": "2025-11-10",
  "time": "14:00",
  "duration": 60,
  "type": "MEETING",
  "recurrence": "NONE",
  "attendeeIds": ["user-id-1", "user-id-2", "user-id-3"],
  "createGoogleMeet": false
}

###
